com.xilinx.rapidwright.edif

Class EDIFParser

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.edif.AbstractEDIFParserWorker
      • com.xilinx.rapidwright.edif.EDIFParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    public class EDIFParser
extends AbstractEDIFParserWorker
implements AutoCloseable
    An EDIF parser created especially for RapidWright. It is only intended to read EDIF generated from Xilinx Vivado. It is not intended to be a fully general purpose EDIF parser. If you have other EDIF that you want to read into RapidWright, load it into Vivado first and then write it out from Vivado. Created on: May 10, 2017
